1954;;The Master Plan;;British;;Cy Endfield;;Norman Wooland, Tilda Thamar;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Master_Plan_(film);;Following WW II, a U.S. army officer stationed in West Germany is assigned with keeping classified information away from the Communists. Unfortunately, Red spies know that he suffers from sudden black-outs and use this to hypnotise him, and make it appear that he is a traitor.[3]